.Sh DESCRIPTION
Serves RESTful (HTTPS) GETs of
.Ar /bx509 and
.Ar /bnegotiate ,
end-points
performing corresponding kx509 and, possibly, PKINIT requests
to the KDCs of the requested realms (or just the given REALM).
